<i>♪ When I was just a little boy ♪</i>

115
00:05:36.301 --> 00:05:38.886
<i>♪ I asked my father ♪</i>

116
00:05:38.887 --> 00:05:40.514
<i>♪ "What will I be?" ♪</i>

117
00:05:42.641 --> 00:05:44.934
