All right. Let's go!

793
00:42:31.931 --> 00:42:33.975
Here you go.

794
00:42:39.939 --> 00:42:41.399
This is it.

795
00:42:43.276 --> 00:42:44.861
This is where
they're buried.

796
00:42:52.035 --> 00:42:52.952
Okay...

797
00:43:02.420 --> 00:43:07.258
[shovels digging in distance]

798
00:43:10.220 --> 00:43:12.263
